{"type": "article", "id": 27028, "title": "车顶帐篷", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-19T07:13:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145403Fd4SqNK5jkx3igR8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你打算来一场自驾野营之旅，这个名为 <a href=\"https://blackfincamperbox.com/\">BlackFin Camper Box</a> 的帐篷或许是个不错的选择。它采用了弹出式的设计，在不超过 30 秒的时间里就能很轻松地将帐篷展开（高度约为 0.9 米），可以舒舒服服地躺进两个人。帐篷的配置也很齐全：可以调节的爬梯、防水材质、透明门帘、可以装衣物的挂钩等等户外标配一应俱全。如果你对这个时髦的帐篷感兴趣的话，可以通过 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1466134845/blackfin-camper-box-hard-shell-roof-top-tent\">Kickstarter</a> 参与众筹，早鸟价为 1695 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145400J8HFu2t9cRm74gIb.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145400U3KANdPtEmTYGBlF.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145401ukqdXvPT79zGIeQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021454025waeKtuOphodyIGq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}